abstract: Third-ranked Maria Sharapova retires from opening match at Wuhan Open against Barbora Strycova due to arm injury; match is Sharapova's first in almost three months and she has missed entire hardcourt season due to leg injury.
lead_paragraph: Competing for the first time in nearly three months, Sharapova retired in the third set of her opening match at China’s Wuhan Open.

headline.main: Maria Sharapova Injured in Her Return
